snippet.title: Enigmata: Stellar War for Mobile Devices 2018
snippet.description:
Here is the full trailer for Enigmata: Stellar War, an exciting new tower defense game for mobile devices. Featuring the music of DJ Mia Lolita. You can play through the App Store here: https://apple.co/2HHBjnC Google Play: https://t.co/9TKERzkVc9

Music: https://soundcloud.com/mia-lolita/
